189
00:13:30,591 --> 00:13:35,231
We've had money to pay off the Jinyin Bank.

190
00:13:35,231 --> 00:13:38,611
We hope they'll show mercy and leave us alone.

191
00:13:38,611 --> 00:13:40,411
Exactly.

192
00:13:41,231 --> 00:13:45,390
