Someone already eliminated them.

193
00:13:45,390 --> 00:13:48,910
Impossible! That's the Power Gang's bank!

194
00:13:48,910 --> 00:13:50,810
True.

195
00:13:54,870 --> 00:14:00,850
Rest assured, no one will oppress you anymore.

196
00:14:02,231 --> 00:14:04,050
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

197
00:14:04,050 --> 00:14:06,710
- You may go.
- Hey, young man.

