216
00:15:36,991 --> 00:15:40,990
Did you see? They destroyed the Jinyin Bank.

217
00:15:45,790 --> 00:15:51,270
 Tang Rou, there's something I must warn you about. 

218
00:15:51,270 --> 00:15:53,591
