219
00:15:53,591 --> 00:15:55,391
 Beware of someone... 

220
00:15:58,270 --> 00:15:59,970
 What? 

221
00:16:02,731 --> 00:16:09,111
 Nothing. Just remember, guard
against anyone holding an umbrella. 

222
00:16:09,111 --> 00:16:11,071
 An umbrella. 

223
00:16:11,071 --> 00:16:14,071
 What? Are you getting superstitious? 

224
00:16:14,071 --> 00:16:20,451
 Besides, it doesn't look like rain. 

225
00:16:20,451 --> 00:16:22,870
 Be serious! I'm not joking. 

226
00:16:22,870 --> 00:16:27,410
 Remember my words.
Watch out for umbrella carriers. Got it? 

227
00:16:27,410 --> 00:16:31,570
 Many people are holding an umbrella.
Who am I supposed to be wary of? 

228
00:16:31,570 --> 00:16:33,731
- Exactly! 
 - Bad people deserve it!

229
00:16:33,731 --> 00:16:36,231
- The rain stopped.
- It did.

230
00:16:36,231 --> 00:16:40,030
No one uses umbrellas when it's not raining.

231
00:16:40,030 --> 00:16:41,930
Move aside!

232
00:16:42,930 --> 00:16:44,571
- The constables!
- The constables!

233
00:16:44,571 --> 00:16:47,031
- Arrest the bad people.
- Take them away!

234
00:16:47,031 --> 00:16:49,670
- Those are the culprits!
- Yes, arrest them all!

235
00:16:50,370 --> 00:16:53,170
- Capture these beasts! That's right.
- Don't move!

236
00:16:54,151 --> 00:16:55,590
