240
00:17:04,270 --> 00:17:05,590
No need to know our names.

241
00:17:05,590 --> 00:17:09,571
We've locked the criminals
in the backyard. Just take them.

242
00:17:10,550 --> 00:17:12,711
The Jinyin Bank has been oppressing the people.

243
00:17:12,711 --> 00:17:18,030
